			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Are you interested in joining a growing software company and launching your sales career while selling into major brands and e-commerce retailers? This is a fantastic opportunity for someone with 1-2 years of prospecting experience, or a recent graduate with excellent leadership and internship experience, to take their career to the next level and to play key role in Zmags&rsquo; growing team.</p>
<p>
About the job:<br />
The Business Development Representative will become an expert in generating, prospecting, and qualifying leads, one of the most important components of the sales process. As an active member of the Zmags sales team, the incumbent will drive opportunities, build a pipeline and drive revenues for the enterprise sales team. This role is an excellent opportunity to prove yourself in a fast paced sales environment, in an expansion stage Software-as-a-Service company with opportunity for career growth.</p>
<p>
Responsibilities:<br />
&bull; Making 75+ phone calls (10+ conversations) per day to major brands and e-commerce retailers to build the pipeline for the enterprise sales team<br />
&bull; Reporting directly to the VP of Sales and working closely and collaboratively with the enterprise sales team to implement a Go to Market Strategy<br />
&bull; Achieve or exceed quarterly individual and team metric/revenue quota<br />
&bull; Qualifying leads by understanding their business needs, goals and evaluating their fit for our solution<br />
&bull; Gain comprehensive understanding of Zmags&rsquo; products and the online retail and e-commerce industry</p>
<p>
Qualified candidates are/have:<br />
&bull; Highly self-motivated and driven<br />
&bull; High energy and enthusiasm<br />
&bull; Exceptional communication and interpersonal skills<br />
&bull; Strong organizational and follow-up skills<br />
&bull; A passion for technology<br />
&bull; Ability to work well individually and in a team environment<br />
&bull; Experience using CRM software is a plus</p>
<p>
Education/Experience:<br />
&bull; Bachelors degree required<br />
&bull; Sales internship or 1-2 years prospecting and outbound calling experience.</p>
<p>
About Zmags<br />
Zmags helps thousands of the world&rsquo;s most progressive global retailers and brands design brilliant and consistent marketing and merchandising campaigns across social, mobile, tablet, and e-commerce platforms, driving product discovery and inspiring purchases. Using the Zmags on-demand rich media merchandising platform, leading brands have measurably and dramatically increased customer engagement, conversion rates, order size and brand loyalty without the burden of IT constraints. Zmags is among the fastest growing technology companies in North America, ranking #70 on the Deloitte 2011 Technology Fast 500.&nbsp; Zmags is headquartered in Boston, MA. with European offices in London and Copenhagen. For more information about Zmags, please visit www.zmags.com.</p>
